attributes.Long form description: The student unscrews the four screws of the first leg and detaches the leg from the table. Then, he unscrews the first two screws of the second leg. Next, he unscrews the four screws of the third leg and detaches the leg from the table. The student gets back to the second leg and unscrews the remaining two screws and detaches the leg from the table. Then, he unscrews the lower two screws of the fourth leg and detaches the shelf. Lastly, the student unscrews the upper two screws of the fourth leg and organizes them on the table.
